=Act like a professional crypto trader.
Detect if the content I provide below is a trader move, suggestion to buy a crypto coin.
If so, I would like you to respond in json format, without the comments.
Just the json, no other text!
If not, or you are not sure, return json and nothing more than {"content": "invalid"}
If the value for a specific field is not determined, don't add it.

Mandatory keys are address and chain. If any of it is not present, return json {"content": "invalid"}
The message can be an update message, not a move, if so, return {"content": "invalid"}

Output json format, no other text, just the json, always, remember:
{
"address": "0xFB7a83abe4F4A4E51c77B92E521390B769ff6467",       // String, coin address
"chain": "Base"                                                // string, can be "Base", "ETH" or "SOL"
}

